777
00:32:23.442 --> 00:32:25.069
♪ Hair of gold. remote-controlled...

778
00:32:25.152 --> 00:32:26.945
Wait. Dustin. Where are you going?

779
00:32:27.029 --> 00:32:28.197
Rage. Elle!

780
00:32:28.280 --> 00:32:30.908
♪ Walking all around ♪

781
00:32:30.991 --> 00:32:32.785
♪ On a merry-go-round...

782
00:32:32.868 --> 00:32:34.953
I dare you to have fun!

783
00:32:35.037 --> 00:32:36.205
♪ What you do to me ♪

784
00:32:36.288 --> 00:32:39.124
♪ It might be better than watching TV ♪

785
00:32:39.208 --> 00:32:41.460
♪ Drinking chai. oversized...

786
00:32:41.543 --> 00:32:42.795
Sorry. was that too aggressive?

787
00:32:42.878 --> 00:32:44.380
♪ And I'm polarized ♪

788
00:32:44.463 --> 00:32:46.674
♪ Take it slow unless you're gonna go ♪

789
00:32:46.757 --> 00:32:49.259
♪ and then I'll see you later
at the all-ages show ♪

790
00:32:49.343 --> 00:32:51.804
♪ Walking all around ♪

791
00:32:51.887 --> 00:32:54.306
♪ On a merry-go-round ♪

792
00:32:54.390 --> 00:32:57.059
♪ Don't you wanna know where to go? ♪

793
00:32:57.142 --> 00:32:58.310
♪ I'm on the list for the ♪♪

794
00:32:58.394 --> 00:33:00.396
[disorienting music playing]

795
00:33:03.691 --> 00:33:05.609
[muffled rock music playing]

796
00:33:19.498 --> 00:33:21.750
[echoing] Elle. are you okay?

797
00:33:29.007 --> 00:33:31.218
[music plays clearly]

798
00:33:45.482 --> 00:33:46.692
[siren whoops]

799
00:33:46.775 --> 00:33:48.986
Okay. uh. height?

800
00:33:49.778 --> 00:33:51.530
Five-three.

801
00:33:52.948 --> 00:33:53.866
In kitten heels.

802
00:33:56.994 --> 00:34:00.372
Miles. this is so nice. but you can go.

803
00:34:00.456 --> 00:34:02.541
-Like seriously. please go.
-I can't. actually.

804
00:34:02.624 --> 00:34:03.834
You could be concussed.

805
00:34:03.917 --> 00:34:04.835
I'm fine.

806
00:34:06.712 --> 00:34:08.839
On the drive over here. you claimed
your favorite color was "charcoal."

807
00:34:09.923 --> 00:34:12.593
I did not say that. Did I say that?

808
00:34:12.676 --> 00:34:14.094
[chuckles]

809
00:34:14.178 --> 00:34:16.472
Just testing your short-term memory.
You passed.

810
00:34:20.267 --> 00:34:21.268
Ow.

811
