I set out to help
an underserved community member

868
00:37:03.639 --> 00:37:07.976
with her comeback
and discovered I was in need of my own.

869
00:37:08.060 --> 00:37:10.354
But comebacks don't happen overnight.

870
00:37:10.437 --> 00:37:11.980
They're hard.

871
00:37:12.064 --> 00:37:15.108
There will be times where it will feel
like everything's against you

872
00:37:15.192 --> 00:37:16.735
and you'll be tempted to give up.

873
00:37:16.818 --> 00:37:18.570
but...

874
00:37:18.654 --> 00:37:19.863
you just can't.

875
00:37:24.743 --> 00:37:28.789
Because Cosmo girls are strong.

876
00:37:28.872 --> 00:37:30.791
and strong people fight.

877
00:37:31.750 --> 00:37:33.126
